summary:
Hi! My name is Pauline Rebel, and I love to write clear and original copy for your website, blog, social media campaign, e-book, or informative white paper. Goal-oriented, search engine friendly, and a perfect fit for your audience. 

✒Check out my portfolio site: www.paulinerebel.com
